{"tid":339494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺信陰陽眼、問米、通靈、投胎呢d野嘅人仲癲過耶撚","createTime":"2017-07-29T06:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T08:06:06.000Z","uid":55851,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7ff5492cae5330ed670ed9e50807674cbded7a1","tid":339494,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T06:16:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/338484/page/13\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/338484/page/13</a><br />\n大開眼界呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n21世紀仲有人問米，仲有人驚農曆七月有鬼，仲有人自稱有陰陽眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n精神病人精彩節錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>#257<br />\n大阪亂四郎　　2 小時前<br />\n西貢果邊好多找代死冤鬼，怨氣係極極極重，重勁過長洲東堤，唔明點解咁多人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好心提醒唔好貪得意近鬼節去新娘潭，東堤果D陰氣重既地方，出左事真係無得怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：自細有陰陽眼 睇過人比x扯落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但唔係西貢</blockquote><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<blockquote>#324<br />\n<strong>大阪亂四郎　　2 小時前</strong><br />\n西貢果邊好多找代死冤鬼，怨氣係極極極重，重勁過長洲東堤，唔明點解咁多人去 <br />\n<br />\n好心提醒唔好貪得意近鬼節去新娘潭，東堤果D陰氣重既地方，出左事真係無得怨 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：自細有陰陽眼 睇過人比x扯落去 但唔係西貢 巴打知唔知仲有邊度陰氣重？我好驚呢味野一般陰氣最重就係戲院，七月十四前少D去海灘游水，好多超渡唔到既會出黎搵食找替死鬼 <br />\n<br />\n好難講曬 你住邊區</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>#322 <br />\n大阪亂四郎  2 小時前<br />\n<br />\n你都戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n首先我係提醒大家 唔係係到嘩眾取寵<br />\n係到做鍵盤戰士有春用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n近近地七月十四前三日夜晚走去藍地水塘游番轉，或者去洪水橋天地人路兜入去，睇到有乜收獲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n#328<br />\n推post_Xander1 小時前<br />\n兩個世界黎 報仇冇話唔得 但對d鬼黎講代價好大</blockquote>"},{"pid":"63c2b45c6957f8dccc0a8a5f8ed88d7708407a8b","tid":339494,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T06:19:33.000Z","msg":"同信動物傳心冇咩分別"},{"pid":"c5dc4684aff016f7e55d838d9b78cec32815d191","tid":339494,"uid":53000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T06:26:17.000Z","msg":"我陪過長輩去問米，啲野講錯哂，笑到我<br />\n問佢有幾多個仔又答錯，<br />\n問佢 我係佢邊個又答錯<br />\n<br />\n不過啲老人家冇讀過書，迷信我都由得佢，<br />\n好多廿幾三十歲大學畢業既同事都迷信,<br />\n我真係打個突，又問米又問神婆，<br />\n結婚又話要跟足時辰八字，又話過大禮唔俾見面，<br />\n如果唔係就會離婚，屌"},{"pid":"365ffa3ef0a61fc43bef2e5e96384e05ae11a131","tid":339494,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T06:31:27.000Z","msg":"星座占星睇相睇掌風水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d330a758ece3165d601f0fe1b02f3e0d91df69","tid":339494,"uid":35236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T06:33:17.000Z","msg":"最迷信既連登仔笑人耶撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c890a1fc9f6814788afbff688e79a009077184c","tid":339494,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T06:37:40.000Z","msg":"怪談"},{"pid":"030f5347f4ecc9d2d76f1a5cfe6f304c9e80110c","tid":339494,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T06:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/144844_e6e304c1c39156be4728170f3124458c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F144844_e6e304c1c39156be4728170f3124458c.jpg&h=7ffeb70f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/144846_578e6ef410f7ea0525edf36fc4353cdc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F14484